dcterms:description: A stylized power system including 3 conventional units, 2 wind farms, and 3 loads, used to evaluate the performance of the proposed UC predictor.

dcterms:description: A larger power system including 19 conventional units, 2 wind farms, 91 loads, and 186 transmission lines, used to assess the computational performance of the proposed UC predictor.
